<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Eden — Wonder Coffee</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --lime:       #A8D635;
  --lime-light: #C8EC5A;
  --lime-pale:  #EEF7CC;
  --green:      #4A7C35;
  --green-deep: #2C5220;
  --green-mid:  #658C3A;
  --white:      #FFFFFF;
  --off-white:  #F5FAE8;
  --yellow:     #F2C846;
  --dark:       #1C2D14;
  --text:       #2E4020;
  --muted:      #6B8B50;
}

*, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--off-white);
  color: var(--dark);
  font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav {
  position: fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0;
  padding: 18px 56px;
  display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
  z-index: 200;
  background: rgba(245,250,232,0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(168,214,53,0.25);
}
.nav-logo {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px; color: var(--green-deep);
  text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}
.nav-logo em { font-style:italic; color: var(--green); }
.nav-links { display:flex; gap:36px; list-style:none; }
.nav-links a {
  font-size: 12px; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color: var(--muted); text-decoration:none; transition: color .25s;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--green); }
.nav-btn {
  background: var(--lime); color: var(--green-deep); border: none;
  padding: 10px 26px; border-radius: 40px;
  font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.1em;
  cursor: pointer; text-decoration:none; transition: all .3s;
}
.nav-btn:hover { background: var(--lime-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #B8DC4A 0%, #D4F060 35%, #F0FAC0 65%, #FFFFFF 100%);
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 100px 56px 60px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden; gap: 40px;
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
  top: -100px; right: -100px; pointer-events:none;
}

.fruit-float {
  position: absolute; font-size: 60px;
  animation: drift linear infinite;
  pointer-events: none;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15));
  user-select: none;
}
.fruit-float:nth-child(1)  { top:8%;  left:5%;  font-size:64px; animation-duration:7s;  animation-delay:0s;   }
.fruit-float:nth-child(2)  { top:12%; right:8%; font-size:72px; animation-duration:9s;  animation-delay:-2s;  }
.fruit-float:nth-child(3)  { top:55%; right:5%; font-size:56px; animation-duration:8s;  animation-delay:-4s;  }
.fruit-float:nth-child(4)  { bottom:10%; left:3%; font-size:52px; animation-duration:10s; animation-delay:-1s; }
.fruit-float:nth-child(5)  { bottom:15%; right:12%; font-size:44px; animation-duration:6s; animation-delay:-3s; }
.fruit-float:nth-child(6)  { top:40%; left:2%;  font-size:36px; animation-duration:11s; animation-delay:-5s; }
.fruit-float:nth-child(7)  { top:22%; left:38%; font-size:32px; animation-duration:8s;  animation-delay:-7s; }

@keyframes drift {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(-3deg); }
  33%      { transform: translateY(-18px) rotate(2deg); }
  66%      { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(-5deg); }
}

.hero-text { position:relative; z-index:10; }

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  border-radius: 40px; padding: 8px 18px;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight:500;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.hero-badge::before { content: '🌿'; font-size:14px; }

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(72px, 10vw, 130px);
  line-height: 0.88; color: var(--green-deep);
  margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--green); display: block; }

.hero-series {
  font-size: 13px; font-weight:500;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color: var(--green-mid); margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.hero-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-bottom: 44px; }
.htag {
  padding: 7px 16px; border-radius:30px;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(74,124,53,0.2);
  color: var(--green-deep); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); transition: all .25s;
}
.htag:hover { background: var(--lime); border-color: var(--lime); }

.hero-cta { display:flex; gap:16px; align-items:center; }

.btn-buy {
  background: var(--green-deep); color: #fff; border:none;
  padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 50px;
  font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase;
  cursor: pointer; text-decoration:none;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44,82,32,0.3); transition: all .3s;
}
.btn-buy:hover { background: var(--green); transform:translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(44,82,32,0.35); }

.btn-learn {
  color: var(--green-deep); font-size:12px; font-weight:500;
  letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; text-decoration:none;
  border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(44,82,32,0.3); padding-bottom:2px; transition: border-color .3s;
}
.btn-learn:hover { border-color: var(--green-deep); }

.hero-product {
  position: relative; z-index:10;
  display: flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
}
.product-img-wrap {
  position: relative;
  animation: floatImg 5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes floatImg {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(-1deg); }
  50%      { transform: translateY(-16px) rotate(1.5deg); }
}
.product-img-wrap img {
  width: 100%; max-width: 400px;
  border-radius: 24px;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 30px 80px rgba(44,82,32,0.35));
}
.product-img-wrap::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; bottom: -30px; left:10%; right:10%; height:40px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(44,82,32,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
  filter: blur(12px);
}
.weight-pill {
  position: absolute; bottom: 20px; right: -10px;
  background: var(--yellow); border-radius: 50px; padding: 12px 20px;
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: 20px; color: var(--dark);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  display: flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; line-height:1.1;
}
.weight-pill small { font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; font-size:10px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.1em; }

/* ── SPECS STRIP ── */
.specs-strip {
  background: var(--green-deep);
  display: flex; overflow: hidden;
}
.spec-cell {
  flex: 1; padding: 40px 36px;
  border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); transition: background .3s;
}
.spec-cell:last-child { border-right:none; }
.spec-cell:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
.spec-key {
  font-size: 9px; letter-spacing:0.3em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color: var(--lime); margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.spec-val {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: 20px; color: #fff; line-height:1.3;
}
.spec-val em { font-style:italic; font-size:16px; opacity:.7; display:block; }

/* ── STORY ── */
.story {
  padding: 120px 80px;
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px; align-items:center;
  background: var(--white); position: relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.sec-tag {
  display: inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
  font-size: 10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.3em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.sec-tag::before { content:''; width:20px; height:2px; background:var(--lime); border-radius:2px; }

.story-title {
  font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 58px); line-height:1.05;
  color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.story-title em { font-style:italic; color:var(--green); }

.story-body { font-size: 15px; line-height:1.9; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 20px; }

.process-cards {
  display: flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1px;
  background: var(--lime-pale); border-radius: 16px; overflow:hidden;
}
.pcard {
  background: #fff; padding: 24px 28px;
  display: flex; gap:20px; align-items:flex-start; transition: background .25s;
}
.pcard:hover { background: var(--off-white); }
.pcard-num {
  width:32px; height:32px; border-radius:50%;
  background: var(--lime-pale); border: 2px solid var(--lime);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--green-deep); flex-shrink:0;
}
.pcard-title { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--dark); margin-bottom:4px; }
.pcard-desc  { font-size:12px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--muted); }

/* ── TASTING ── */
.tasting {
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #EEF7CC 0%, #F5FAE8 60%, #fff 100%);
  padding: 100px 80px;
}
.tasting-inner {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:80px; align-items:start;
}
.tasting-title {
  font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px,4vw,56px); line-height:1.05; margin-bottom:32px;
}
.tasting-title em { font-style:italic; color:var(--green); }

.flavor-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.flavor-card {
  background: #fff; border-radius:16px; padding:20px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(168,214,53,0.2);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(74,124,53,0.06); transition: all .3s;
}
.flavor-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(74,124,53,0.12); border-color:var(--lime); }
.flavor-emoji { font-size:28px; margin-bottom:10px; display:block; }
.flavor-name { font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--dark); letter-spacing:.08em; margin-bottom:4px; }
.flavor-note { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.5; }

.variety-note { background: var(--green-deep); color:#fff; border-radius:16px; padding:28px 32px; }
.variety-note h4 { font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif; font-size:22px; color:var(--lime); margin-bottom:12px; }
.variety-note p { font-size:13px; line-height:1.8; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

.flavor-visual {
  position:relative; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:420px;
}
.fw-ring {
  position:absolute; border-radius:50%; border:1px dashed rgba(74,124,53,0.15);
}
.fw-ring-1 { width:380px; height:380px; }
.fw-ring-2 { width:260px; height:260px; }
.fw-ring-3 { width:140px; height:140px; }
.fw-center {
  position:relative; z-index:5; text-align:center;
  width:110px; height:110px; border-radius:50%;
  background: var(--lime);
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(74,124,53,0.2);
}
.fw-center-title { font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif; font-size:13px; color:var(--green-deep); line-height:1.2; }
.fw-dot {
  position:absolute; text-align:center; transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
}
.fw-dot-circle {
  width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--lime); margin:0 auto 5px;
  box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(168,214,53,0.2);
}
.fw-dot-label {
  font-size:10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--green-deep); white-space:nowrap;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.85); padding:3px 8px; border-radius:20px;
}

/* ── STORAGE ── */
.storage {
  background: var(--lime); padding: 60px 80px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:48px;
}
.storage-icon { font-size:56px; flex-shrink:0; filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(44,82,32,0.2)); }
.storage-key { font-size:10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.3em; text-transform:uppercase; color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom:10px; }
.storage-heading { font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif; font-size:30px; color: var(--green-deep); margin-bottom:8px; }
.storage-desc { font-size:13px; line-height:1.8; color: var(--green); }

/* ── ORDER ── */
.order {
  background: var(--green-deep);
  padding: 120px 80px; text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.order::before {
  content:'EDEN';
  position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif; font-size:280px; line-height:1;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); white-space:nowrap; pointer-events:none;
}
.order-fruit {
  position:absolute; font-size:48px; opacity:.12;
  animation: drift linear infinite; pointer-events:none;
}
.order-fruit:nth-child(1){ top:10%; left:5%;  animation-duration:8s;  }
.order-fruit:nth-child(2){ top:15%; right:8%; animation-duration:11s; animation-delay:-3s; }
.order-fruit:nth-child(3){ bottom:12%; left:8%; animation-duration:9s; animation-delay:-5s; }
.order-fruit:nth-child(4){ bottom:10%; right:6%; animation-duration:7s; animation-delay:-2s; }

.order-tag {
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;
  font-size:10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.3em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--lime); margin-bottom:24px;
}
.order-tag::before,.order-tag::after { content:''; width:28px; height:1px; background:var(--lime); opacity:.5; }

.order-title {
  font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;
  font-size:clamp(54px,8vw,100px); line-height:.9; color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px;
}
.order-title em { font-style:italic; color:var(--lime); }
.order-sub { font-size:13px; letter-spacing:.1em; color:rgba(255,255,255,.4); margin-bottom:52px; }

.order-btns { display:flex; gap:16px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }

.btn-order-main {
  background:var(--lime); color:var(--green-deep); border:none;
  padding:18px 52px; border-radius:50px;
  font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:700;
  letter-spacing:.15em; text-transform:uppercase;
  cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none;
  box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(168,214,53,0.3); transition: all .3s;
}
.btn-order-main:hover { background:var(--lime-light); transform:translateY(-3px); }

.btn-order-ghost {
  background:transparent; color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
  padding:18px 52px; border-radius:50px;
  font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:400;
  letter-spacing:.15em; text-transform:uppercase;
  cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none; transition: all .3s;
}
.btn-order-ghost:hover { border-color:var(--lime); color:var(--lime); }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer {
  background: var(--dark); padding: 36px 80px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
}
.footer-logo { font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif; font-size:20px; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; }
.footer-logo em { font-style:italic; color:var(--lime); }
.footer-copy { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:.2em; color:rgba(255,255,255,.2); }

/* ── REVEAL ── */
.reveal { opacity:0; transform:translateY(28px); transition: opacity .75s ease, transform .75s ease; }
.reveal.vis { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }

@media (max-width:900px){
  nav { padding:16px 24px; }
  .nav-links { display:none; }
  .hero { grid-template-columns:1fr; padding:100px 24px 48px; }
  .hero-product { order:-1; }
  .product-img-wrap img { max-width:300px; }
  .specs-strip { flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .spec-cell { flex:0 0 50%; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); }
  .story { grid-template-columns:1fr; padding:60px 24px; }
  .tasting { padding:60px 24px; }
  .tasting-inner { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .storage { padding:40px 24px; flex-direction:column; }
  .order { padding:80px 24px; }
  footer { padding:28px 24px; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; text-align:center; }
}

  


  /* ── STORY BANNER GIF ── */
  .story-banner {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 56px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(44,82,32,0.15);
    line-height: 0;
  }
  .story-banner img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Wonder <em>Eden</em></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#story">Story</a></li>
    <li><a href="#tasting">Tasting</a></li>
    <li><a href="#specs">Details</a></li>
    <li><a href="#order">Order</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#order" class="nav-btn">Buy Now</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <span class="fruit-float">🍎</span>
  <span class="fruit-float">🥝</span>
  <span class="fruit-float">🍋</span>
  <span class="fruit-float">🫐</span>
  <span class="fruit-float">🍍</span>
  <span class="fruit-float">🍊</span>
  <span class="fruit-float">🌿</span>

  <div class="hero-text">
    <div class="hero-badge">Specialty Coffee · Chiang Rai · Since 2009</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Wonder<em>Eden</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-series">Kombucha Series — Natural Scoby Selected</p>
    <div class="hero-tags">
      <span class="htag">Light Roast</span>
      <span class="htag">Cartimor</span>
      <span class="htag">1,200 m.a.s.l.</span>
      <span class="htag">200 g</span>
      <span class="htag">SCOBY Fermented</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#order" class="btn-buy">Order Now</a>
      <a href="#story" class="btn-learn">Our Story ↓</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-product">
    <div class="product-img-wrap">
      <img src="eden_nobg.png" alt="Eden Coffee Bag">
      <div class="weight-pill">200<small>gram</small></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Story Banner GIF - full width -->
  <div class="story-banner" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
    <img src="eden_banner.gif" alt="Eden Coffee in motion">
  </div>

</section>

<div class="specs-strip" id="specs">
  <div class="spec-cell">
    <div class="spec-key">Origin</div>
    <div class="spec-val">Chiang Rai <em>Thailand</em></div>
  </div>
  <div class="spec-cell">
    <div class="spec-key">Variety</div>
    <div class="spec-val">Cartimor</div>
  </div>
  <div class="spec-cell">
    <div class="spec-key">Process</div>
    <div class="spec-val">Natural <em>SCOBY Selected</em></div>
  </div>
  <div class="spec-cell">
    <div class="spec-key">Altitude</div>
    <div class="spec-val">1,200 m.a.s.l.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="spec-cell">
    <div class="spec-key">Roast Level</div>
    <div class="spec-val">Light Roast</div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="story" id="story">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="sec-tag">Our Journey</div>
    <h2 class="story-title">A <em>Fermentation</em><br>Like No Other</h2>
    <p class="story-body">
      Wonder Coffee has been cultivating specialty coffee in the highlands of Chiang Rai since 2009. Our Cartimor variety grows at 1,200 metres above sea level — and we process it in a way no one else does.
    </p>
    <p class="story-body">
      We adapted SCOBY — the living culture of bacteria and yeast famous for fermenting kombucha — to work on coffee cherries. The result transforms Cartimor's natural character into something extraordinary.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay:.15s">
    <div class="process-cards">
      <div class="pcard">
        <div class="pcard-num">01</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pcard-title">Cartimor Cherry Harvest</div>
          <div class="pcard-desc">Hand-picked at peak ripeness in the Chiang Rai highlands at 1,200 m.a.s.l.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pcard">
        <div class="pcard-num">02</div>
        <div>
          <div class="pcard-title">SCOBY Inoculation</div>
          <div class="pcard-desc">A carefully selected Symbiotic Culture of Bacteria and Yeast is introduced to the coffee cherries.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pcard">
        <div class="pcard-num">03</div>
